{
  "stem": "4272.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later, when I was a little older, I think I would have gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Probably would have gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What were your goals as a young girl growing up in Poland?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In what way?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For your future.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, God, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did I give it much thought?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I have to think about it, really, whether I gave it much thought at the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were so busy with everyday life, with-- with meeting ends and-- and all that that, that as a young-- a young girl, we didn't think about it and didn't worry about it too much.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was it difficult for your father to make a living then?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very difficult.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very difficult.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was a private school and he had to pay tuition.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sometimes it was not enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow he managed, kept us all in school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After school, where you able to work at all?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did work shortly before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- the reason for this was because they-- they revoked the-- the right to have the school open.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So most of the students that were in school then were left without the school, without anything to do.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to Warsaw and I got a job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I applied also to a state school-- state high school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at first, they said yes, they would have room in my grade, and yes I can apply.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now to apply, at the time, was 15 zlotys, which was an awful lot of money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A family could almost live a whole week on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but then when I filled out the papers and they saw my last name, Zylbersztejn, there was no doubt that I couldn't be anything else but Jewish.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
